# VTable Connected Lines Example

Output "connected-lines.gif"

Set FontSize 16
Set Width 800
Set Height 500
Set Shell "bash"

Type "go run ."
Enter
Sleep 2s

# Expand nodes to create a nested structure
Enter
Sleep 500ms
Down@500ms
Enter
Sleep 500ms
Down@500ms
Down@500ms
Enter
Sleep 1s

# Cycle through connector styles
Type "l"
Sleep 1s
Type "l"
Sleep 1s
Type "l"
Sleep 1s
Type "l"
Sleep 1s
Type "l"
Sleep 1s
Type "l"
Sleep 1s
Type "l"
Sleep 2s

# Quit the application
Type "q"
Sleep 1s 